data.description: The property at 4483 Catalina Circle in East Point, GA offers a convenient location near the airport, making travel accessibility a plus.   A beautiful, fenced backyard at a property like this adds privacy and outdoor space for enjoyment. It can be an appealing feature for relaxation, entertaining, or simply enjoying the outdoors without leaving the comfort of home.  Original hardwood floors can bring character and charm to a home. They often add a timeless appeal and can serve as a unique feature that enhances the property's overall aesthetic. This home features ample space and only stove and dishwasher amenities, though it's worth noting that it doesn't include a garage. Its proximity to transportation hubs and its favorable location makes it an attractive option for those seeking accessibility and convenience.
